#### Day 42: Week 6 Integration — Your Multi-Tool Workflow

📖 **Concept:** You now know how to combine text, images, voice, code, automation, and research. Time to build your signature workflow.

🔨 **Exercise (20 min):**
1. Map your ideal multi-tool workflow for your most important project
2. Prompt: *"I want to build a workflow that [goal]. I have access to [list your tools]. Design the optimal multi-tool workflow — what tool for each step, how they connect, and how to automate what I can."*
3. Document it. This is your playbook.

