#### Day 48: AI for Operations & Efficiency

📖 **Concept:** The unsexy side of AI that makes the biggest difference: operational efficiency. Process documentation, SOPs (Standard Operating Procedures), training materials, scheduling optimization, inventory management, and workflow improvement. This is where AI saves REAL money.

