#### Day 50: AI for Education & Mentoring

📖 **Concept:** You now have skills that most people don't. Every prompting technique, every workflow, every tool — these are skills you can teach. AI for education isn't just about learning; it's about building systems that help others learn.

🔨 **Exercise (20 min):**
1. Create a mini-course on ONE AI skill you've mastered
2. Prompt: *"Help me design a 30-minute workshop teaching [AI skill] to complete beginners. Include: a simple explanation, a live demonstration, a hands-on exercise, and a take-home resource. Make it so engaging that even skeptics will be impressed."*
3. Plan to deliver this workshop — at work, at church, at a community center, or online

👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 **Family Bonus:** Let your kids "teach" AI skills to their friends. Teaching is the highest form of learning.

