📖 **Concept:** Your community has problems AI can help solve. Local nonprofits that need marketing help. Schools that need educational resources. Community organizations that need better communication. Senior centers that need technology assistance. Food banks that need logistics optimization. The skills you've built are exactly what these organizations need but can't afford.

