3. Send the proposal. Or just show up and offer to help.

👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 **Family Bonus:** Choose a family cause. Apply AI skills together to create something for that cause — marketing materials, educational content, fundraising letters, event planning.

🔗 **Resource:** [DataKind](https://www.datakind.org/) — Data science + AI volunteering for social good.

💭 **Reflection:** *"Service isn't what I do. It's who I am." With AI, how much more service can you do?*

