#### Day 111: Building Your AI Legacy — The Long View

📖 **Concept:** Legacy isn't about fame. It's about impact that outlasts you. The teacher whose students remember her 40 years later. The volunteer whose food bank still feeds families after he's gone. The parent whose values live on in their children's choices. AI amplifies legacy: the systems you build can help people long after you stop building. The knowledge you share can propagate forever.

🔨 **Exercise (25 min):**
1. Define your legacy:
   *"Help me think about my AI legacy. Not my business. Not my career. My LEGACY. When I look back on my life 20 years from now, what do I want to have contributed to the world through AI? Who do I want to have helped? What do I want to have built that outlasts me? Help me articulate this in a way that's deeply personal, not generic."*
2. Create your "Legacy Plan":
